    "body": "Managing your subscription Your Subscription settings show your current plan and give you a self-service billing portal for everything money-related. See your current plan The Subscription section of your account shows the plan your organization is on. What's included depends on your plan — your Storyraise contact can walk you through the options if you're considering a change. Manage billing and subscription Click Manage billing and subscription to open your secure billing portal. There you can: Update your payment method. View and download invoices and receipts. Review your current plan and billing schedule. Change or cancel your subscription. The portal is hosted by our payment processor, so your card details are handled securely and are never stored in Storyraise. Need help with billing? For plan changes, renewals, or questions a self-service portal can't answer, reach out to your Storyraise contact or our support team . If your subscription has lapsed and you'd like to come back, get in touch — we'll get you set up again. Related Organization settings Setting up your account"
